text: Mohammad Ilyas (born 25 June 1996) is a Pakistani cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Lahore Blues in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam Trophy on 16 September 2018. He made his List A debut for Lahore Blues in the 2018–19 Quaid-e-Azam One Day Cup on 22 September 2018. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Pakistani cricketers Category:Lahore Blues cricketers Category:Cricketers from Lahore
